title: Pixel 5G and Sky (UK} Mobile Service Question
content:
When the Pixel 5G is launched.
Is this going to be compatible with 5G on Sky (UK) Operator which runs on the O2 Network.

Currently I'm using a Sky (UK) Mobile SIM on a Pixel 2 and it's impossible to get a 4G Connection, only LTE is available.

When I used to have an EE SIM in the Pixel 2 4G worked fine, but it seems there is an incompatability issues with 4G and Sky (UK) in being able to get 4G.

I know it's probably too early to say but thought I'd ask anyway....
